# {project-name} — Environment Variables

# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in real values.
# NEVER commit .env. Use a secrets manager (see docs/secrets.md).

# Example:
# DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@localhost:5432/mydb
# API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# ── Optional ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets manager integration ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# If using Infisical (self-hosted):
#   INFISICAL_API_URL=https://your-infisical.example.com
#   Run: infisical run -- <your-command>
#
# If using Doppler:
#   Run: doppler run -- <your-command>
#
# If using SOPS+age:
#   Run: sops exec-env .env.enc <your-command>
